,"iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/7guWbUNeA6IVpFgcONDeXNybS0P.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/sPXJCy9KQpk4S96f8jCzP3MVl0r.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1500,"height":843,"file_path":"/77rRbmgE84tSHclRG6ekXteQTH6.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.779,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/8lR49ixQTVmAeyCE6kLflodmbBd.jpg","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1536,"height":864,"file_path":"/kK3GT0tfKoXIDvXr2zSUdrNgQD5.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:09:44.616+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Rabbit Without Ears","runtime":116,"tagline":"You always meet twice...","homepage":"","overview":"Rainbow press reporter Ludo is sentenced to 8 months, but is released on probation. But he has to work 300 hours for a local daycare center and meets Anna who has unfinished business with him."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":111,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Klatsch- und Boulevard-Reporter Ludo ist zuweilen etwas \"kreativ\" bei der Gestaltung seiner Artikel und schrammt damit oft nur haarscharf an Ärger vorbei. Als er jedoch bei einer Hochzeit (im wahrsten Sinne des Wortes) unangemeldet hereinplatzt ist das Maß voll. Ludo landet vor Gericht und die Richterin verdonnert ihn zu 300 Stunden Sozialarbeit in einem Kindergarten. Unglück im Unglück: Die Leiterin dort ist Anna, die als Kind mit Brille und Zahnspange gesegnet, lange unter den bissigen Kommentaren von Mädchenschwarm Ludo leiden musste. Sie erkennt ihn, er sie nicht. Für Ludo bricht eine Zeit der Leiden an - und für Anna die Zeit der Rache? Oder kommt es für beide ganz anders?"},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Красавчик","runtime":110,"tagline":"Может встретимся?","homepage":"","overview":"Журналист Людо, схлопотавший восемь месяцев тюрьмы, освобожден на испытательный срок при условии, что он обязательно пройдет курс трудотерапии. Ему предстоит отработать триста часов в местном детском саду. Как ухаживать за 8-летними оболтусами, Людо не очень представляет, но в группе работает его старая знакомая — еще в школе он изводил ее своими выходками."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Un conejo sin orejas","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nora Tschirner interpreta a una tímida profesora de preescolar cuyo cuadriculado mundo se desmorona cuando, tras montar un tremendo escándalo en una boda, un paparazzo es condenado a 300 horas de trabajos para la comunidad y tiene que cumplirlas precisamente junto a ella. El problema es que el paparazzo en cuestión, Ludo (Til Schweiger), fue compañero suyo de colegio y se dedicaba a hacerle la vida imposible. Claro que, bien pensado, quizá ésta sea una ocasión perfecta para ajustar cuentas con él... siempre y cuando el amor, tan meticón él, no se entrometa."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"300 ore per innamorarsi","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"La vita del di Ludo, reporter di cronaca rosa, scorre all'insegna del divertimento. Insieme al paparazzo Moritz, è sempre a caccia di scoop sulle celebrità di turno, e le sue relazioni durano al massimo una notte. Ma quando è trascinato in tribunale da un vip dello spettacolo dovrà affrontare il lato serio della vita..."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"甜蜜幼儿园","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"专栏作家Ludo（蒂尔·斯威格饰）及其老友——摄影师Moritz（马提亚斯·施维赫夫饰)均是玩世不恭的花花公子，两人终日追逐明星的足迹打探他们的隐私。不过，Ludo的好日子就快到了头，他因违法而被法庭判处了300小时的社区服务令——必须在一间幼儿园里老老实实“服刑”。 　　女主角Anna（诺拉·茨切纳饰）正是这间幼儿园的老师，也是Ludo的旧日相识，不过以前那个四眼钢牙常被Ludo捉弄的小女生如今已经出落得亭亭玉立。仇人相见好戏连篇，一段浪漫的爱情故事同时也在悄悄酝酿……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Fülenincs nyúl","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ludo lesifotós, cimborájával fáradhatatlanul keresik a sztárok, sztárocskák és celebek nagy vagy rossz pillanatait. Néha még maga is elhiszi a fotók mellé tálalt történeteit, ám egyszer pórul jár. Egy áldozata feljelenti, és végül egy óvodában letöltendő, 300 órányi szociális munkára ítélik. Ez már Anna  terepe, aki gyerekkora óta utálja Ludót, s így minden pillanatot megragad, hogy törlesszen. Végül Ludo is belátja, hogy a pletykarovaton túl is van élet."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Красунчик","runtime":0,"tagline":"Люди зустрічаються двічі","homepage":"","overview":"Журналіст Лудо, отримавши вісім місяців в'язниці, був звільнений на випробувальний термін за умови, що він обов'язково пройде курс трудотерапії. Йому належить відпрацювати триста годин в місцевому дитячому садку. Як доглядати за 8-річними телепнями, Лудо не дуже уявляє, але в групі працює його стара знайома - ще в школі він діставав її своїми витівками. І ось тепер та соплива дівчинка виросла, перетворившись практично в супермодель. А що робити з моделями, Лудо в курсі. Але у дівчини свої плани на старого знайомого ..."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Zajíček bez oušek","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ludo je novinář oblíbeného bulvárního plátku, Anna učitelka ve školce. Ačkoliv Ludo dnes stěží vzpomene jméno, natož vzezření tmavovlasé obrýlené dívky s rovnátky, kterou v dětství úspěšně šikanoval, Anna si malého trapiče pamatuje dobře. Když Ludo jednoho dne zaklepá na vrátka mateřské školky, aby zde odsloužil trest za zpackanou reportáž, Anna neváhá a vrací sebevědomému novináři vše i s úroky. Koneckonců, málokteré místo je k ponížení Luda právě tak vhodné, jako školka plná vřískajících dětí. Plánovanou pomstu však začínají komplikovat city, do nichž se oba hrdinové pozvolna zaplétají."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Aprendendo a Amar","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Keinohrhasen","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ludo Decker est journaliste people à Berlin. Avec son ami photographe, Moritz, il travaille pour le tabloïd Das Blatt. Ludo est un don Juan qui se sert de son travail pour rencontrer de nouvelles conquêtes. À la suite d'un reportage qui a mal tourné, il écope de 300 heures de travaux d’intérêt général dans une garderie. Il y retrouve une de ses anciennes camarades de classe, Anna Gotzlowski, qui en est la directrice.\r Lui ayant servi de souffre-douleur à l'école à l'époque, Anna décide de profiter de l’occasion pour se venger ; Ludo ne peut rien pour l’en empêcher et se sert de ce nouveau « travail » pour séduire la mère d’une des petites filles dont il s’occupe. Les tensions entre Ludo et Anna finissent par se dissiper et tous deux deviennent amis : Ludo offre à Anna une peluche qu’il a faite lui-même, un lapin sans oreilles."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Плюшко-безушко","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Бонвиванът и репортер за булевардно издание Лудо Декер с пълна сила се наслаждава на живота си - до момента, когато е осъден да положи социален труд в детска градина и се налага изцяло до промени поведението си. Детската учителка Ана не понася самовлюбеното му поведение и му поставя единствено неприятни задачи. По всичко личи, че двамата няма да се разберат в този живот, докато в един момент всичко се обръща наопаки..."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Aprendendo a Amar","runtime":116,"tagline":"Você sempre se vê duas vezes ... (Você sempre se encontra duas vezes ...)","homepage":"","overview":"Ludo Decker é um fútil repórter sensacionalista que vive em Berlim. Sua rotina diária é espionar e descobrir fofocas das celebridades para um tablóide. Ele também se aproveita do seu trabalho para conquistar as mulheres. Quando Ludo e seu fotógrafo estão espionando uma festa de noivado, eles quebram o domo de vidro da casa por acidente e caem em cima do bolo. Ludo é condenado a prestar 300 horas de serviço comunitário em uma creche. Lá ele conhece Anna, sua vizinha de infância, que era sempre ridicularizada por ele. Como vingança, ela o escolhe para os mais humilhantes trabalhos. Porém com o convívio, a tensão entre os dois se dissipa e eles se tornam mais que amigos, fazendo com que Ludo descubra como dar valor às coisas que realmente importam e encontre o verdadeiro sentido do amor."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Miłość z przedszkola","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Reporter Ludo (Til Schweiger) oraz paparazzi Moritz (Matthias Schweighofer) obracają się ciągle w świecie gwiazd i gwiazdeczek. Zdarza się, że Ludo sam wierzy w sklecone przez siebie opowiastki, co pewnego dnia obraca się przeciwko niemu - sędzia skazuje go na 300 godzin prac społecznych w świetlicy dla dzieci. Tu natomiast rządzi Anna (Nora Tschirner), która nie mogła znieść naszego lowelasa już w dzieciństwie. Ludo musi więc przejść przez piekło, ale w końcu odkryje samego siebie..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Kulaksız Tavşan","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Çapkın bir paparazzi olan Ludo, ünlü bir futbolcunun nikahını kendine has yöntemlerle görüntüler ve bu yüzden mahkemelik olur.. Hakim Ludo’ya verilecek 8 ay hapis cezasını, 300 saat bir anaokulunda çalışmasına karar verir. Bu anaokulunda Anna ile karşılaşır.. ve olaylar komik şekilde devam eder.."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ludo is een journalist die voor het Duitse roddelblad Das Blatt werkt. Hij is altijd onderweg met zijn fotograaf Moritz om kiekjes te nemen van bekende mensen. Hij verzint echter verhalen en wordt veroordeeld tot 300 uur sociaal werk. Hij moet zijn uren uitzitten in een kinderopvangcentrum waar hij een oude bekende tegenkomt: Anna, een meisje met wie hij vroeger op school zat en die hij eigenlijk altijd uitlachte en plaagde. Anna geeft hem daarom allerlei saaie taken. Maar stilletjes aan raken ze toch bevriend en zelfs verliefd."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"귀 없는 토끼","runtime":115,"tagline":"300시간이면 바람둥이 완전접수!","homepage":"","overview":"한번 포착된 기사거리는 ‘절대’ 놓치지 않는다! 그러나….  이 여자는 ‘제발(?)’ 놓치고 싶다!!  연애는 하룻밤 엔조이 전문, 취재는 파파라치 전공인 가십지 기자 ‘루도’(틸 슈바이거).  호텔 옥상에서 유명인사의 약혼식을 몰래 취재하다 엉덩이를 깐 채(?) 웨딩케이크에 처박히고 만다! 법원으로부터 선고 받은 300시간 동안 유치원에서 꼼짝없이 일해야 하는 그가 맞닥뜨린 상대는 바로…. 초딩시절, 루도의 괴롭힘에 치를 떨던 안나.  사랑을 고대하지만 ‘우먼센스’ 제로인 안나가 ‘플레이보이’ 루도에게 복수의 칼을 가는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Bezuchí zajkovia","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Novinár Ludo je za zničenie strechy luxusného hotela odsúdený na verejnoprospešné práce v materskej škôlke, kde sa po rokoch opäť stretáva s Annou, ktorú ako malú šikanoval. Tá je rozhodnutá mu všetko vrátiť aj s úrokmi..."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"沒有耳朵的兔子","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"有緣，就會愛上兩次…\r 沒有女友，狗仔記者路多最需要什麼？首先，他最需要一些八卦爆料，其次就是屬於自己的一夜情。但不論是獨家八卦或是性感美女，憑著男人性好冒險和堅定不移的自信，他總能手到擒來…。\r 路多的生活簡直太美好了，直到他出了個大紕漏。有次他追蹤獨家八卦時，竟不慎從五星級飯店屋頂失足跌落，一絲不掛地趴在一場世紳名媛的豪華婚宴上，而遭到了法院的判決：罰他去一家幼稚園，執行300個小時的志工服務。路多以為這只是個很小兒科的處罰，直到他驚訝發現這幼稚園的園長，竟是他的小學同學安娜；而小時候戴了付大眼鏡、看來超呆的安娜，就經常遭到他的惡整…。\r 果然是風水輪流轉，安娜終於有機會扳回一城！她總算可以盡情的、堅定的、替天行道的報仇了！安娜時而質疑路多沒幫兔子玩偶縫上兩片耳朵，時而譏笑他是幼稚園史上最機車的志工…，飽受責難的路多做多錯多、衰運連連；但，他卻漸漸開始愛上了這些「折磨」…。路多喜歡幫小朋友繫緊鞋帶，也喜歡跟他們講鬼故事、玩躲貓貓，但他更愛天天被安娜找碴…。然而，有個秘密就快隱藏不住了：安娜發現自己竟情不自禁地愛上了路多，並衷心希望這300個小時，永遠都不要結束…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"ლამაზმანი","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ჟურნალისტი ლოუდო, რომელსაც რვა თვის პატიმრობა შეუფარდეს, განთავისუფლებულია გამოსაცდელ ვადაზე პირობით, რომ ის აუცილებლად გაივლის შრომის–ტერაპიის კურსებს. მას მოუწევს სამასი საათი იმუშავოს ადგილობრივ საბავშვო ბაღში."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"沒有耳朵的兔子","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"有緣，就會愛上兩次… 沒有女友，狗仔記者路多最需要什麼？首先，他最需要一些八卦爆料，其次就是屬於自己的一夜情。但不論是獨家八卦或是性感美女，憑著男人性好冒險和堅定不移的自信，他總能手到擒來…。 路多的生活簡直太美好了，直到他出了個大紕漏。有次他追蹤獨家八卦時，竟不慎從五星級飯店屋頂失足跌落，一絲不掛地趴在一場世紳名媛的豪華婚宴上，而遭到了法院的判決：罰他去一家幼稚園，執行 300 個小時的志工服務。路多以為這只是個很小兒科的處罰，直到他驚訝發現這幼稚園的園長，竟是他的小學同學安娜；而小時候戴了付大眼鏡、看來超呆的安娜，就經常遭到他的惡整…。 果然是風水輪流轉，安娜終於有機會扳回一城！她總算可以盡情的、堅定的、替天行道的報仇了！安娜時而質疑路多沒幫兔子玩偶縫上兩片耳朵，時而譏笑他是幼稚園史上最機車的志工…，飽受責難的路多做多錯多、衰運聯聯；但，他卻漸漸開始愛上了這些「折磨」…。路多喜歡幫小朋友繫緊鞋帶，也喜歡跟他們講鬼故事、玩躲貓貓，但他更愛天天被安娜找碴…。然而，有個秘密就快隱藏不住了：安娜發現自己竟情不自禁地愛上了路多，並衷心希望這 300 個小時，永遠都不要結束…。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":9511,"adult":false,"title":"Rabbit Without Ears 2","video":false,"overview":"Two years have passed. There is a normal life, but handsome Ludo meets his old love, and Anna is very jealous...","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7752,"vote_count":272,"poster_path":"/vULrURaizz6FNHVmObbPPzFlA3R.jpg","release_date":"2009-11-24","vote_average":5.735,"backdrop_path":"/slXaQ221FgSOsmAOqB7GQpHHjod.jpg","original_title":"Zweiohrküken","original_language":"de"},{"id":53174,"adult":false,"title":"Kokowääh","video":false,"overview":"Henry is a playboy who has no idea that he is the father of a beautiful, cute girl out of a One-night-Stand. Her mother left the daughter in front of Henry door after her husband realized after 8 years of marriage that he is not the father so their relationship now is breaking up... By the way: Kokowääh, is how a German (in this case an 8 Year old child) that has never heard the dish before - would pronounce \"Coq Au Vin\" (chicken in a wine sauce).","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8567,"vote_count":295,"poster_path":"/s1xlGUJhPlqRa1FF6Uw73UXuEUS.jpg","release_date":"2011-02-03","vote_average":6.257,"backdrop_path":"/oIFtnPkM3jqbq4kGlEjhARvhIxo.jpg","original_title":"Kokowääh","original_language":"de"},{"id":114438,"adult":false,"title":"Russendisko","video":false,"overview":"Three young Russian friends, who move from Moscow to Berlin in a lucky wave of emigration right after the fall of the Berlin wall. They take their chance looking for a better life and find themselves involved in the tales of everyday lunacy on the streets of Berlin and its spirit of the early nineties.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.279,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/34vwgjaGT0ILmKQaWo31PumjoLY.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-28","vote_average":5.43,"backdrop_path":"/g2kCzCm1nJy0pO4Ku5kSQDVYSVY.jpg","original_title":"Russendisko","original_language":"de"},{"id":223993,"adult":false,"title":"Rabbit Without Ears and Two-Eared Chick","video":false,"overview":"The no-ear bunny can do everything just as well as the other bunnies. But because he has no ears, nobody wants to play with him. When one day an egg is left on his doorstep, he has no idea that this is the start of a wonderful friendship. He experiences many exciting adventures with the two-eared bunny, right up to the fulfillment of their greatest wishes. Because if you have a real friend, you can do anything. And have a lot of fun doing it.","genre_ids":[16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3602,"vote_count":21,"poster_path":"/rbKMsASYx4sd9wA6U1mrUPj4iP7.jpg","release_date":"2013-09-26","vote_average":5.548,"backdrop_path":"/361Tk7OXzSTjHzg1hczpBfZUtAi.jpg","original_title":"Keinohrhase und Zweiohrküken","original_language":"de"},{"id":9321,"adult":false,"title":"The Polar Bear","video":false,"overview":"Four characters become involved in one dramatic story: Nico has a mission to drive a car containing a live bomb to a specified destination, park the car and escape as quickly as she can. Leo has become his client's target, having carried out a \"contract\" that unfortunately had already been cancelled. Fabian and Reza want to enjoy themselves without any money, bringing themselves into contact sooner or later with the police. Sooner or later all four will meet up in dramatic circumstances....","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3167,"vote_count":38,"poster_path":"/9F1selwsaWrzScQIsNupbYuvdIv.jpg","release_date":"1998-11-12","vote_average":6.342,"backdrop_path":"/9enlW5RxOb6vAkoEuqb1XIerFqU.jpg","original_title":"Der Eisbär","original_language":"de"},{"id":301225,"adult":false,"title":"Standby","video":false,"overview":"Twenty-something Alan (Gleeson) is down on his luck. Stood up at the altar and recently fired from his banking job, he finds himself working with his mother as a part-time tourist advisor at Dublin Airport. It's there he comes face to face with first love Alice (Paré), stuck on standby for a flight home to New York. Their summer romance ended eight years previously with Alan promising to return to the US one day. He never did, and they haven't spoken since. Seizing his chance, Alan convinces a reluctant Alice to stay one more night in Dublin. Over the course of an unforgettable evening, they may just realise that they are more compatible than ever. But time is running out on this brief encounter. When does an unexpected second chance, become the one you've always been looking for?  - Written by Wildcard Distribution","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2474,"vote_count":37,"poster_path":"/sCtH2uita7BGP9ohGt7yNmbAz8r.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-14","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/A3sUt0LwEZYW15Xc75wqFtBiXda.jpg","original_title":"Standby","original_language":"en"},{"id":41441,"adult":false,"title":"The Sword with No Name","video":false,"overview":"Mu Myeong is a Joseon dynasty headhunter who meets and falls in love with lady Ja Yeong who will become the future Empress Myseongseong. A few years later, Ja Yeong enters the royal palace to marry King Gojong. Mu Myeong still having feelings for Ja Yeong and in an attempt to get closer to her becomes her personal body guard.","genre_ids":[18,28,36,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5506,"vote_count":53,"poster_path":"/gzC2wata6kthYyni1gb6jjVTcSP.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-24","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/fN6E5gfRuxR2QbYinLWEcNh5gCe.jpg","original_title":"불꽃처럼 나비처럼","original_language":"ko"},{"id":265787,"adult":false,"title":"Kennen Sie Ihren Liebhaber?","video":false,"overview":"Victoria Stellmann, head of a traditional cruise shipping company, leads a happy but routine family life. But then she meets the charming Jacques and gets involved in an affair. The angry awakening does not leave long to wait, her lover proves to be an unscrupulous blackmailer. He threatens to publish a video of her night of love. Victoria starts to flee to the front.","genre_ids":[18,80,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0921,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/ckCfS1hPRSa6cwKwDdsbdeOfHsT.jpg","release_date":"2012-01-12","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":"/kYwd2oaDioxemfCkM0j3WEL60EL.jpg","original_title":"Kennen Sie Ihren Liebhaber?","original_language":"de"},{"id":85058,"adult":false,"title":"First Monday in October","video":false,"overview":"For the first time in history a woman is appointed to the U.S. Supreme Court, where she becomes a friendly rival to a liberal associate.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1212,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/8a4K7e83WoCTOwje4LEhTwtOu0a.jpg","release_date":"1981-08-21","vote_average":6.056,"backdrop_path":"/kIJRhonhWUJr764c5S7Wu4kvwZw.jpg","original_title":"First Monday in October","original_language":"en"},{"id":796497,"adult":false,"title":"Meeresleuchten","video":false,"overview":"Thomas Wintersperger, a man who has to learn to deal with his grief, sees his loss as an opportunity to reorganize his life.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1982,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/oT9xYxdcaBIYoO8ab0zXZsvPPhK.jpg","release_date":"2021-02-17","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/zq0ComyPb0Pd5HN9qsp1fHTMb9E.jpg","original_title":"Meeresleuchten","original_language":"de"},{"id":32679,"adult":false,"title":"Times Change You","video":false,"overview":"After the bestselling book comes the film about Germany's most successful rapper: authentic, provocative and radical. Despite all his successes, Bushido has to face the demons of his past again and again.","genre_ids":[10402,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5002,"vote_count":69,"poster_path":"/iQg5KvJl7D44m7Vq1X4lsOnwteu.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-04","vote_average":4.188,"backdrop_path":"/cxbD9HzwCwTZG7ZzX11I4KMHLUa.jpg","original_title":"Zeiten ändern Dich","original_language":"de"},{"id":6733,"adult":false,"title":"Where Is Fred?","video":false,"overview":"In order to catch a basketball from the favorite team of his girlfriend's spoiled son, Fred poses as a numb, wheelchair-bound fan. But when he catches the ball, he also catches the attention of young, attractive filmmaker Denise, who wants to feature an invalid fan in an image film for the team. Fred has to keep playing his role, while real invalid and really furious fan Ronny might call his bluff at any moment. Worse, still, love sets in...","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4079,"vote_count":140,"poster_path":"/9DkMHl3XHEYRBUXCOm3WVbmBn8G.jpg","release_date":"2006-11-15","vote_average":6.254,"backdrop_path":"/bu3haiMt2ML5NmO8WOhGbw0j08X.jpg","original_title":"Wo ist Fred?","original_language":"de"},{"id":1915,"adult":false,"title":"Manta, Manta","video":false,"overview":"A not-so-clever guy called Bertie with an Opel Manta (a low-budget European sports coupé from the '80s) gets competition in a street race from a guy with a fast Mercedes, and another slick guy with a Ferrari tries to get his hands on Bertie's girlfriend.","genre_ids":[35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7574,"vote_count":159,"poster_path":"/cHBEudYatUvo6T6R5W1NtvQNUVe.jpg","release_date":"1991-10-03","vote_average":5.733,"backdrop_path":"/lbwhLH0rQQj9GYwZBwSOBFmxcUu.jpg","original_title":"Manta, Manta","original_language":"de"},{"id":11248,"adult":false,"title":"Fatherland","video":false,"overview":"Fictional account of what might have happened if Hitler had won the war. It is now the 1960s and Germany's war crimes have so far been kept a secret. Hitler wants to talk peace with the US president. An American journalist and a German homicide cop stumble into a plot to destroy all evidence of the genocide.","genre_ids":[18,53,28,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8147,"vote_count":129,"poster_path":"/sSOyk8fWs2sN7YHXsbsp5ZxcGG5.jpg","release_date":"1994-11-26","vote_average":6.147,"backdrop_path":"/znWxInJXM4GZ3SzMYbfRZMjlEtQ.jpg","original_title":"Fatherland","original_language":"en"},{"id":21910,"adult":false,"title":"I Sell the Dead","video":false,"overview":"18th century justice catches up with a pair of grave robbers. With only a few hours to go before his date with the guillotine, Arthur Blake tells his life story to Father Francis Duffy. Before long, Arthur spills the beans on how he got started in the grim corpse peddling business with seasoned ghoul Willie Grimes.","genre_ids":[35,18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5559,"vote_count":200,"poster_path":"/1KjIGzUho6NCE7dDJP1QyRnMRRK.jpg","release_date":"2008-08-07","vote_average":5.983,"backdrop_path":"/9lPCj5JIgw5UJhtMOJ3L09vmS0H.jpg","original_title":"I Sell the Dead","original_language":"en"},{"id":23512,"adult":false,"title":"The Boys Are Back","video":false,"overview":"When the wife of sports-writer Joe Warr dies of cancer, he takes on the responsibility of raising their 6-year-old son, and his teenage son from a previous marriage. As Joe rejects the counsel of his mother-in-law and other parents, he develops his own philosophies on parenting.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4647,"vote_count":188,"poster_path":"/6sIPtMC5GxLrsSXgdMHXJf8X4qV.jpg","release_date":"2009-09-25","vote_average":6.314,"backdrop_path":"/sbrDFDBT7xizvnOmrXoIScAnAtv.jpg","original_title":"The Boys Are Back","original_language":"en"},{"id":22309,"adult":false,"title":"The Fighting Temptations","video":false,"overview":"Darrin Hill, a slick-talking but down-on- his-luck NYC advertising exec, returns to his hometown in Georgia to claim the inheritance his aunt left him. But before Darrin can collect the money, he must fulfill his aunt's final wish -- to create a local choir.","genre_ids":[35,10402,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2687,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/1Dd8TBA6G0n1x2N8KpJvIefy2sB.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-19","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/ttizthyI5mRIVxHsv6p6eS0GiKi.jpg","original_title":"The Fighting Temptations","original_language":"en"},{"id":130747,"adult":false,"title":"The Guardians","video":false,"overview":"15-year-old Nina witnesses a terrible crime that puts her life in danger. Being an orphan, she has nobody she can trust. When corrupt businessman Thomas Backer sends five killers after Nina, witness protection officer, Max, a former special-forces soldier, is responsible for her safety. They soon overcome their initial distance to find common ground. While on the run from the ruthless Backer, Rudi, one of Max’s former comrades, comes to their rescue – and continues to help the two out of some precarious situations. Even Max’s ex-girlfriend Sara is not just there to help him as a federal prosecutor. Nevertheless, Nina and Max face ever-increasing danger, and soon the teenager is not the only one in need of a guardian angel – Max could use one too.","genre_ids":[18,28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1139,"vote_count":117,"poster_path":"/dQGAy7RVgGXdejRgLP8NzC2Op9Z.jpg","release_date":"2012-09-18","vote_average":6.081,"backdrop_path":"/sQGHdkl0dnHRnA6EpFXlq1R0T78.jpg","original_title":"Schutzengel","original_language":"de"},{"id":347666,"adult":false,"title":"We Need to Talk","video":false,"overview":"Nuria is a young girl with a good life, a boyfriend to marry him and a parents who love her, but a problem: she still is married with Jorge. Former CEO, Jorge lives almost in the ruin together his ex boss and friend Lucas. After two years separated, Jorge doesn't forget her, but Nuria tries to ask him files for divorce when she wrongly discovers that Jorge has tried to commit suicide jumping by a window. Feeling responsible by it, Nuria talks with her parents Miguel and Patricia, according cheat Jorge for that he beliefs that they aren't divorced and Miguel didn't lose his company due to the Jorge's bad business inversions that ruined his parents-in-law, in order to get the divorce without pain for anybody. The real problem is what when the lies accumulate, the situation is each time more dangerously out of control.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2792,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/rkHj0IzLI1bHZOyrnnKD3aUkY3R.jpg","release_dat