":"The Harrad Experiment","original_language":"en"},{"id":3008,"adult":false,"title":"10:30 P.M. Summer","video":false,"overview":"A female traveling companion seduces a married man and his alcoholic wife.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.2696,"vote_count":28,"poster_path":"/zEEifnz7dswBLA5hAIBe2xTHRaj.jpg","release_date":"1966-10-24","vote_average":5.179,"backdrop_path":"/w4eANiESWzXXSoLgLDnLUr9We2P.jpg","original_title":"10:30 P.M. Summer","original_language":"en"},{"id":3084,"adult":false,"title":"Wuthering Heights","video":false,"overview":"Young orphan Heathcliff is adopted by the wealthy Earnshaw family and moves into their estate, Wuthering Heights. Soon, the new resident falls for his compassionate foster sister, Cathy. The two share a remarkable bond that seems unbreakable until Cathy, feeling the pressure of social convention, suppresses her feelings and marries Edgar Linton, a man of means who befits her stature. Heathcliff vows to win her back.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":6.3192,"vote_count":305,"poster_path":"/pwHdSzXwlUFAcYGcFutKcPcX2OW.jpg","release_date":"1939-04-07","vote_average":7.169,"backdrop_path":"/qWSWJnq38eVYrMzs6YkxRT8yMYK.jpg","original_title":"Wuthering Heights","original_language":"en"},{"id":6538,"adult":false,"title":"Charlie Wilson's War","video":false,"overview":"A Texas congressman sets a series of events in motion when he conspires with a CIA operative to aid Afghan mujahideen rebels fighting the Soviets.","genre_ids":[35,18,36],"popularity":3.1345,"vote_count":1610,"poster_path":"/45FghqcdSYRWK7PsHUInaFPNd8l.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-19","vote_average":6.538,"backdrop_path":"/6MyFH4phzKMxdvuk8ZfI1fohMz7.jpg","original_title":"Charlie Wilson's War","original_language":"en"},{"id":1059572,"adult":false,"title":"New Dimension! Crayon Shin-chan the Movie: Battle of Supernatural Powers ~Flying Sushi~","video":false,"overview":"40-years ago, there was a prophecy claiming that in the year of “20” and “23”, two emitting 